  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>The creature you specify becomes attuned to the cheering of their allies, warding away fatigue and pains. Anyone within 30 feet of the target can take a single audible, mental action to call out encouragingly to the target while the spell persists, restoring 12 hit points. Once a creature has cheered a creature on, they can't do so again for that creature until the start of their next turn.</p><hr /><p><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> The hit points restored increases by 6. @Damage[(6*@item.level)[healing]]{Heightened Healing}</p><p><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> The duration of the spell is no longer sustained and is just one minute.</p><p><strong>Heightened (+2)</strong> An additional target can be specified.</p>",
